          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Responsible Disposal Reauthorization Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill extends through FY2031 authorization for the Department of Energy to operate the Cheney disposal cell in Mesa County, Colorado. (The disposal cell serves as a repository for mill tailings, which is sandy waste that results from the process of turning natural uranium into fuel.)</p>]]></text>
